        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " also), not of hearsay, of which, moreover, the passages in Kypke are not to be explained. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Who",
